\hat{\text{revenue}} = -33.63 + 0.9 \cdot \text{clicks} + 95.51 \cdot \text{display}
\]final model demonstrates improved fit compared initial full model. Residual Standard Error (RSE), measures typical prediction error, decreased approximately 93.82 72.29, indicating improved accuracy. R-squared (\(R^2\)) value increased 62% 77%, suggesting greater proportion variability revenue now explained selected predictors.
